html(lang='en')
  head
    title Welcome to Twit-Padi
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons', rel='stylesheet')
    link(type='text/css', rel='stylesheet', href='materialize/css/materialize.min.css', media='screen,projection')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='css/style.css')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
  body
    header
      nav.light-blue.accent-3
        .container
          .nav-wrapper
            a.brand-logo.white-text(href='/') Twit-Padi
            a.button-collapse.right(href='#', data-activates='mobile-demo')
              i.white-text.material-icons menu
            ul.right.hide-on-med-and-down
              li
                a.white-text(href='/about') About
              li
                a.white-text(href='/help') Help
            ul#mobile-demo.side-nav
              li
                a(href='/about') About
              li
                a(href='/help') Help
    main.main-area
      .container
       h3 About
       br
       h5 Easily find Non-Followers 
       p Hunting through your twitter account and finding those who don't follow back can be a tough task, well it used to be with this simple tool you generate a list of those who you follow but do not follow back.
       br
       h5 Unfollow Non-Followers
       p Easily locate and remove people who don't follow back your account and stop following them immediately by going to their profile from this tool and clicking on unfollow.
       br
       h5 Follow New Followers back
       p Track all your people who follow your twitter account but are yet to be followed back. Simply visit their profile from this tool and follow them.
